  "key": "C# major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "Oh, you got me thinking about it all I still feel you and your words from all the\nabyss that you brought on me The words you say are nice at first\nWe find that's just not where it's at It's not the truth\nWhen it's always tit for tat You're not to blame, well, that's a shame\nI hear your voice from the echoes of the abyss\nMy heart, it did not miss Your touch, that painful bliss\nI don't miss it A blessing in disguise\nOh, it's gonna be over soon, yeah\nThere's gonna be truth here There's gonna be truth here\nEchoes, echoes There's gonna be a truth in the dark\nThere's truth in the part that makes you rise up and be more\nthen you could ever think to be here\nAnd now we find All the lies that you said\nAll the things that you took from me Of the, of the abyss\nEchoes Echoes\nTalked to my fears, said, you don't live here\nRent free  fear, said, cool, but you'll never exempt me\nChains in my cadence, but pain is a rhythm\nTurn every wound into bars, now I’m with ’em they say know your place\nSaid, watch me erupt from a spark in the dark to a nuclear\nThrust If silence is death, I'm immortal in sound\nEvery time I speak, Im unearthing the ground\nEcho In my sound, I'll suffocate the lies I hate\nI'm done being small for your comfortable fate\nI hit bottom, found a mic in a grave,  turned  panic into power\nNow I'm louder than the pain you caused\nAll the nights that you lost on me\nScream into the void\nTill it bleeds my name\nI found my truth in the static, found my God in the flame\nI was silent, surviving, now I'm paranoid\nWith a voice sharp enough to cut through your void\nAs I scream into the void\nIt all collapses, turns the abyss into light\nWatch the dark, practice if you're waiting for the sign\nThis is it, you don't need anything but just to be you\nYeah, And find your voice, it comes from the abyss in us\nIt all comes from the abyss and us\nAnd us",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 19.040000915527344,
      "text": "Oh, you got me thinking about it all I still feel you and your words from all the",
      "start": 3.5199999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 24.260000228881836,
      "text": "abyss that you brought on me The words you say are nice at first",
      "start": 19.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 30.68000030517578,
      "text": "We find that's just not where it's at It's not the truth",
      "start": 25.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 36.63999938964844,
      "text": "When it's always tit for tat You're not to blame, well, that's a shame",
      "start": 30.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 41.70000076293945,
      "text": "I hear your voice from the echoes of the abyss",
      "start": 36.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 46.81999969482422,
      "text": "My heart, it did not miss Your touch, that painful bliss",
      "start": 41.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 51.2599983215332,
      "text": "I don't miss it A blessing in disguise",
      "start": 46.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 54.7599983215332,
      "text": "Oh, it's gonna be over soon, yeah",
      "start": 51.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 62.060001373291016,
      "text": "There's gonna be truth here There's gonna be truth here",
      "start": 57.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 66.22000122070312,
      "text": "Echoes, echoes There's gonna be a truth in the dark",
      "start": 63.439998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 69.5,
      "text": "There's truth in the part that makes you rise up and be more",
      "start": 66.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 78.37999725341797,
      "text": "then you could ever think to be here",
      "start": 69.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 85.81999969482422,
      "text": "And now we find All the lies that you said",
      "start": 79.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 92.87999725341797,
      "text": "All the things that you took from me Of the, of the abyss",
      "start": 85.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 114.05999755859375,
      "text": "Echoes Echoes",
      "start": 113.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 115.91999816894531,
      "text": "Talked to my fears, said, you don't live here",
      "start": 114.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 118.87999725341797,
      "text": "Rent free  fear, said, cool, but you'll never exempt me",
      "start": 116
    },
    {
      "end": 121.81999969482422,
      "text": "Chains in my cadence, but pain is a rhythm",
      "start": 118.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 124.80000305175781,
      "text": "Turn every wound into bars, now I’m with ’em they say know your place",
      "start": 121.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 128.74000549316406,
      "text": "Said, watch me erupt from a spark in the dark to a nuclear",
      "start": 125.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 131.9600067138672,
      "text": "Thrust If silence is death, I'm immortal in sound",
      "start": 129.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 134.86000061035156,
      "text": "Every time I speak, Im unearthing the ground",
      "start": 131.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 141.36000061035156,
      "text": "Echo In my sound, I'll suffocate the lies I hate",
      "start": 134.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 147.94000244140625,
      "text": "I'm done being small for your comfortable fate",
      "start": 141.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 154.5,
      "text": "I hit bottom, found a mic in a grave,  turned  panic into power",
      "start": 149.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 161.0800018310547,
      "text": "Now I'm louder than the pain you caused",
      "start": 154.5
    },
    {
      "end": 166.0800018310547,
      "text": "All the nights that you lost on me",
      "start": 161.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 176.24000549316406,
      "text": "Scream into the void",
      "start": 170.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 181.0800018310547,
      "text": "Till it bleeds my name",
      "start": 178
    },
    {
      "end": 186.9199981689453,
      "text": "I found my truth in the static, found my God in the flame",
      "start": 182.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 190.9199981689453,
      "text": "I was silent, surviving, now I'm paranoid",
      "start": 186.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 197.9199981689453,
      "text": "With a voice sharp enough to cut through your void",
      "start": 191.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 206.24000549316406,
      "text": "As I scream into the void",
      "start": 201.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 212.36000061035156,
      "text": "It all collapses, turns the abyss into light",
      "start": 206.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 218.0800018310547,
      "text": "Watch the dark, practice if you're waiting for the sign",
      "start": 212.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 224.10000610351562,
      "text": "This is it, you don't need anything but just to be you",
      "start": 218.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 231.4600067138672,
      "text": "Yeah, And find your voice, it comes from the abyss in us",
      "start": 224.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 238.36000061035156,
      "text": "It all comes from the abyss and us",
      "start": 232.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 243.74000549316406,
      "text": "And us",
      "start": 242.36000061035156
    }
  ],
